data.description: Mountain views in Clear Creek Estates. Property uses a private well and septic system. A propane powered furnace was installed 1 year ago and with a walk in crawl space / cellar area, the indoor cellar and the seperate 2 car garage / shop give this mountain Gem a perfect getaway and mountain retreat.  This home is located on a 1.67 acre lot which is mostly flat ground & would be great for a horse or two. Great views while sitting on the covered deck.
